{"tid":1816943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動POST] 完美通報系統: 哨子吊墜, 緊急情況就吹, 全民請準備!","createTime":"2020-01-08T16:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T18:40:07.000Z","uid":216683,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"90447292b4e6e7ffb0699dd08da3cb6fe98986f5","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"無論你係街坊定做哨兵<br />\n又或者係前線<br />\n又或者係後排<br />\n<br />\n都要有一個哨子吊墜, 帶條頸鏈出街唔撚得?<br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLOwafD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLOwafD.jpg&h=fb3b9b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原因十分之清晰簡單<br />\n<br />\n有狗黎就一定要吹<br />\n你諗住自己把聲夠大聲叫, 一嗌大家就知咩事?<br />\n你諗住見到狗, 報料上D GROUP到, 大家一定睇得切?<br />\n你諗住聽到有人話, 有狗! 你就知班狗係咩方位跑緊黎?<br />\n<br />\n我答你<br />\n1. 吹哨子好大聲, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遠嘅都會聽到</span></strong><br />\n2. 哨子可以有節奏,<span style=\"color: red;\"> 節奏可以表達到危急程度</span><br />\n3. 吹哨子可以分方位, <span style=\"color: red;\">知道邊個方向有狗</span><br />\n<br />\n我知有人不嬲都帶緊, 但普及程度唔高<br />\n同埋最重要嘅一樣野係<br />\n班狗宜家係會中段突入, 唔再係之前係前面推進<br />\n所以所有和理非都要幫手, 帶個哨子<br />\n見到有危急情況就要吹響佢<br />\n<br />\n有用POST, 永遠都唔會有人推<br />\n又或者推到咁上下過咗一晚<br />\n大家都當無睇過咁<br />\n<br />\n今晚就要推到俾大家都睇到!!!!<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>所有人, 同我帶哨子出街, 邊個唔帶邊個就係鬼</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外,  申請人身保護令係一個解決濫捕市民嘅完美方案, 係差班民主派唔做野<br />\n個POST已經有哂TEMPLATE, 係差洗民主派版, 迫佢地做野, <br />\n千幾個LIKE都無人幫手去洗版<br />\n自己入去睇, 有哂案例同方法, 要叫DEAD BODY楊岳橋起身做野, 唔好再扮死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1812105/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1812105/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"351bab9c80b14591cee510aee0073c2f1e594baa","tid":1816943,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"邊買"},{"pid":"3bfcd11cbf9bd6ff71629ad228efd21eaf764c7d","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"我知大家都睇緊美國總統全國講話<br />\n我都係<br />\n但大家一邊睇一邊推啦好嗎<br />\n<br />\n我呢個POST一定上硬熱門<br />\n因為我知呢個方面一定有用<br />\n一直都有做緊, 係差在個普及性<br />\n<br />\n宜家班狗嘅進攻角度已經唔同哂<br />\n係要靠全民做哨架啦<br />\n<br />\n靠把聲? 靠個GROUP?<br />\n不如用個哨子即時通報仲好<br />\n<br />\n幫手推"},{"pid":"fb613f4664785766e4e0ac15ac171627f15fba09","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"351bab9c80b14591cee510aee0073c2f1e594baa","tid":1816943,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"邊買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"要睇下你追求D咩野<br />\n有人要型要潮流<br />\n你咪揀D型棍D<br />\n<br />\n想要老土D, 又或者想COSPLAY教練, 你去買中學體育老師個D哨都得"},{"pid":"92b96f2f387226888469b13c78d6a25a9d2b4879","tid":1816943,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb613f4664785766e4e0ac15ac171627f15fba09","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"351bab9c80b14591cee510aee0073c2f1e594baa","tid":1816943,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"邊買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"要睇下你追求D咩野<br />\n有人要型要潮流<br />\n你咪揀D型棍D<br />\n<br />\n想要老土D, 又或者想COSPLAY教練, 你去買中學體育老師個D哨都得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊度買呀<br />\n咩鋪頭會有"},{"pid":"49937253746f6abb055e217bd56386897746e9a9","tid":1816943,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:14:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n進擊の巨人<br />\n入面有信號煙通訊教學<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"85d7119c3bdbc84e09c725a797aff03f4b9cc601","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:14:52.000Z","msg":"要型,要潮咪買呢D款<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFGqeNH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgFGqeNH.jpg&h=0177c2f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鍾意COSPLAY, 扮球證嘅咪呢款<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhy4vma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhy4vma.jpg&h=9c678ab3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cecee6bb8fd2b35f07d59ac735b19bf1c7ac93e","tid":1816943,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"好早已經有人講過，但問題係一有人鳩吹就會引起混亂，同埋就算吹左都唔知咩事"},{"pid":"975662eb78bd83d1b7782653ec667c447c3cb2a5","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/-/_/R-p-13504?mc=8027255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.decathlon.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fp%2F-%2F_%2FR-p-13504%3Fmc%3D8027255&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=b5c4f955\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/-/_/R-p-13504?mc=8027255</a><br />\n球證個類, 24蚊有一個<br />\n<br />\n要款個D, 旺中行一轉大把"},{"pid":"3feedfc895a94cfacf364334089bc3b8234eabf9","tid":1816943,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"351bab9c80b14591cee510aee0073c2f1e594baa","tid":1816943,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"邊買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"文具鋪可能有"},{"pid":"4454315ee979ef9366e05abfdf2af7288b8a06a6","tid":1816943,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:18:02.000Z","msg":"如果有臥底亂鳩咁吹或黑警響集會時四圍吹咁點？"},{"pid":"91f463b617fa8753ad61faa3de382674e9cd3523","tid":1816943,"uid":73143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"完美？求其搵條友鳩吹玩鳩你都得啦"},{"pid":"09a06f66072caa747c0ffb6119101196337f4e57","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cecee6bb8fd2b35f07d59ac735b19bf1c7ac93e","tid":1816943,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"好早已經有人講過，但問題係一有人鳩吹就會引起混亂，同埋就算吹左都唔知咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"亂?<br />\n亂得過, 一堆勁高音嘅女聲係到嗌, 走呀! 咁樣?<br />\n<br />\n一黎唔知方位<br />\n二黎其實遠D聽, 係聽唔到佢講咩<br />\n<br />\n正如你嗌一二一二<br />\n你會有個BEAT<br />\n<br />\n另外一個超大問題要解決<br />\n就係好似上星期咁, 成班狗突入HSBC個邊<br />\n遠處有人想報有狗, 成班叫緊口號根本聽唔到<br />\n只有雞聲先搞得掂<br />\n<br />\n暫時我諗到呢個方法係OK, 唔知你仲有冇一個更好諗法<br />\n幫手諗下<br />\n<br />\n要嘅係極速, 又可以通報得遠嘅方法"},{"pid":"21b8ff96e64d9ca3f16e5543003b480a51a95d22","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91f463b617fa8753ad61faa3de382674e9cd3523","tid":1816943,"uid":73143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"完美？求其搵條友鳩吹玩鳩你都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"你行行下見到隔離條友鳩吹, 你唔會問佢咩事<br />\n反而係扮睇唔到, 之後繼續行?<br />\n<br />\n反問返你<br />\n遊行期間, 突然有個人係一個街口到亂叫<br />\n走呀! 走呀! 之後跑走<br />\n咁呢個問題你點解決?<br />\n<br />\n班狗搵條友鳩跑鳩叫玩鳩你都得啦?"},{"pid":"0d43e4ab270da09cd86ecd8b55a9cf30c547b32e","tid":1816943,"uid":73143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21b8ff96e64d9ca3f16e5543003b480a51a95d22","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91f463b617fa8753ad61faa3de382674e9cd3523","tid":1816943,"uid":73143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"完美？求其搵條友鳩吹玩鳩你都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"你行行下見到隔離條友鳩吹, 你唔會問佢咩事<br />\n反而係扮睇唔到, 之後繼續行?<br />\n<br />\n反問返你<br />\n遊行期間, 突然有個人係一個街口到亂叫<br />\n走呀! 走呀! 之後跑走<br />\n咁呢個問題你點解決?<br />\n<br />\n班狗搵條友鳩跑鳩叫玩鳩你都得啦?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"你未出過黎架？不嬲都有班撚樣鳩嗌架啦"},{"pid":"12dcc5672fc279869612f1ae7ace79bad5a59ba6","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d43e4ab270da09cd86ecd8b55a9cf30c547b32e","tid":1816943,"uid":73143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21b8ff96e64d9ca3f16e5543003b480a51a95d22","tid":1816943,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91f46