短<br />\nS.O.S摩斯密碼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"現場聽過一定知我講乜野<br />\n急緊後退嘅話<br />\n哨子聲完全令你知道背後面個情況係點<br />\n<br />\n遠到近<br />\n慢到快"},{"pid":"9750e55310392646c9e1c3b04fee2f08fcd3e4fb","tid":1816943,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"準備好啦"},{"pid":"53528979f1bf4f116586e553019ec1f310d50d03","tid":1816943,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:58:04.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"f73ac26c5ed8d04b048c6eb11333f2b05e314411","tid":1816943,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:29:44.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"9e76c7f23bb4042d5fd9bdf90a8f4cb5c11de06b","tid":1816943,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"根本啲驚弓之鳥係唔係都話有狗"},{"pid":"5c49ab7a942d387be4ec9f1f7eff090e3718551d","tid":1816943,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"銀雞，<br />\n吹完啲狗會聽你講嘢。"}]}